  "events": [],
  "notes": "Mt. Mortar 2F Inside (20x18 blocks, 40x36 tiles, confirmed: MountMortar2FInside.blk = 360 bytes). The upper interior floor of Mt. Mortar — accessed from the north end of 1F Outside or from within 1F Inside. This floor has water pools navigable by Surf and a waterfall area (Waterfall HM required to access the upper sections where the Dragon Scale and Escape Rope are found). One trainer: Super Nerd Hugh (Seadra Lv39 with Smokescreen, Twister, Surf, Waterfall) — Hugh's partner Markus is on 1F Inside and mentions a trainer with a Seadra that knows Waterfall. Six visible pokeball items: Max Potion, Rare Candy, TM49 Defense Curl, Dragon Scale (key evolution item for Seadra->Kingdra), Elixir, Escape Rope. One hidden Full Restore. The Dragon Scale on this floor combined with Hugh's Seadra creates an intentional connection — the player can obtain the item to evolve their own traded Seadra. Tileset: TILESET_DARK_CAVE. Music: MUSIC_UNION_CAVE."
